void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = vec4(ivec4(0, 0, 0, 0));
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;
    u_xlat2.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat2.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].z;
    u_xlat1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat2, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].x;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].z;

    u_xlat5.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat5.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w;
    u_xlat5.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;

    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat5, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz;
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat4.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat4.z = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat23 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat23 = max(u_xlat23, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat23 = inversesqrt(u_xlat23);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat23) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat18.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.xy;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat18.xy * u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat18.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat18.xy = u_xlat18.xy + u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat5.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat19.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat19.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat4.zw = u_xlat18.xy;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_12.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_12.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat5.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.yzw = u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat4;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_2;

    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;

}

    u_xlat70 = u_xlat16_115;
    u_xlat108 = max(_DstBlendFactor, 0.0);
    u_xlat108 = min(u_xlat108, 1.0);
    u_xlat146 = (-u_xlat32.x);
    u_xlat70 = u_xlat146 + u_xlat70;
    u_xlat70 = u_xlat70 * u_xlat108;
    u_xlat32.x = u_xlat70 + u_xlat32.x;
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat32.x;
    u_xlat16_27.xyz = u_xlat16_27.xyz;
    u_xlat16_27.xyz = u_xlat16_27.xyz;
    u_xlat16_27.xyz = u_xlat16_27.xyz;
    u_xlat16_27.xyz = u_xlat16_27.xyz;
    u_xlat16_27.xyz = u_xlat16_27.xyz;
    u_xlat16_27.xyz = u_xlat16_27.xyz;
    u_xlat16_27.xyz = u_xlat16_27.xyz;
    u_xlat33.x = float(2.50999999);
    u_xlat33.y = float(2.50999999);
    u_xlat33.z = float(2.50999999);
    u_xlat34.x = float(0.0299999993);
    u_xlat34.y = float(0.0299999993);
    u_xlat34.z = float(0.0299999993);
    u_xlat35.x = float(2.43000007);
    u_xlat35.y = float(2.43000007);
    u_xlat35.z = float(2.43000007);
    u_xlat36.x = float(0.589999974);
    u_xlat36.y = float(0.589999974);
    u_xlat36.z = float(0.589999974);
    u_xlat37.x = float(0.0799999982);
    u_xlat37.y = float(0.0799999982);
    u_xlat37.z = float(0.0799999982);

    u_xlat16_30.y = float(0.449999988);

    u_xlat16_30.xyz = u_xlat16_27.xyz * u_xlat16_30.xyz;
    u_xlat30.xyz = u_xlat16_30.xyz;
    u_xlat33.xyz = u_xlat30.xyz * u_xlat33.xyz;
    u_xlat33.xyz = u_xlat34.xyz + u_xlat33.xyz;
    u_xlat33.xyz = u_xlat30.xyz * u_xlat33.xyz;
    u_xlat34.xyz = u_xlat30.xyz;
    u_xlat35.xyz = u_xlat30.xyz * u_xlat35.xyz;
    u_xlat35.xyz = u_xlat36.xyz + u_xlat35.xyz;
    u_xlat34.xyz = u_xlat34.xyz * u_xlat35.xyz;
    u_xlat34.xyz = u_xlat37.xyz + u_xlat34.xyz;
    u_xlat33.xyz = u_xlat33.xyz / u_xlat34.xyz;
    u_xlat34.xyz = vec3(ivec3(100, 100, 100));
    u_xlat33.xyz = min(u_xlat33.xyz, u_xlat34.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33.xyz = u_xlat33.xyz;

    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;

    u_xlat2.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;

    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;

    u_xlat33.y = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.yw);

    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;

    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.zw;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.zw = u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat7.zw = u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;

    u_xlat16_18.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_18.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_18.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz;

    u_xlat6.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat6.x;

    u_xlat16_2.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz;

    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;

    u_xlat16_4.z = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.w = float(0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    vs_TEXCOORD9 = u_xlat8;
    vs_TEXCOORD11 = u_xlat16_4;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].z;
    u_xlat1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat2, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].x;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].z;
    u_xlat5.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w;
    u_xlat5.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat5.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w;
    u_xlat5.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat2.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat5, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat4 = in_TANGENT0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat4.www * u_xlat6.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat6.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat6.z = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = max(u_xlat38, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].x;
    u_xlat6.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;
    u_xlat6.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat7.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat7.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat8.xw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].yz;
    u_xlat8.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat8.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat6.x = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat7.z = u_xlat8.x;
    u_xlat6.y = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat6.z = dot(u_xlat8.yzw, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = max(u_xlat38, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yzx;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat3.yzx * u_xlat6.yzx;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat3.zxy * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = float(0.5);
    u_xlat6.y = float(0.5);
    u_xlat30.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat31.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat31.xy = u_xlat31.xy + u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.y;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat38 * _Time.x;
    u_xlat9.y = float(0);
    u_xlat33.xy = vec2(ivec2(0, 0));
    u_xlat16_10 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.z + _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.x;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat10.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat10.xy = (-u_xlat33.xy);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat32.x = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat8.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat8.y = (-u_xlat32.x);
    u_xlat8.xw = u_xlat8.xw;
    u_xlat8.z = u_xlat32.x;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat8.xz);
    u_xlat10.y = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat8.yw);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.z;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat32.x = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat8.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat8.y = (-u_xlat32.x);
    u_xlat8.xw = u_xlat8.xw;
    u_xlat8.z = u_xlat32.x;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat33.xy, u_xlat8.xz);
    u_xlat10.y = dot(u_xlat33.xy, u_xlat8.yw);
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat33.xy;

    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat10.xy;

    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.y;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat38 * _Time.x;
    u_xlat9.y = float(0);
    u_xlat33.xy = vec2(ivec2(0, 0));
    u_xlat16_11 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.z + _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat11.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat10.xy = (-u_xlat33.xy);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat10.xy;

    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);

    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));

    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);

    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;

    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat33.x = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat33.y = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.zw;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;

    u_xlat8.zw = u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat7.zw = u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_18.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_18.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.yzw = u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;

    u_xlat16_4.y = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.z = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.w = float(0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    vs_TEXCOORD9 = u_xlat8;
    vs_TEXCOORD11 = u_xlat16_4;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = float(0.5);
    u_xlat6.y = float(0.5);
    u_xlat30.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat31.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat31.xy = u_xlat31.xy + u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.y;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat38 * _Time.x;
    u_xlat9.y = float(0);
    u_xlat33.xy = vec2(ivec2(0, 0));
    u_xlat16_10 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.z + _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.x;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat10.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat10.xy = (-u_xlat33.xy);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat32.x = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat8.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat8.y = (-u_xlat32.x);
    u_xlat8.xw = u_xlat8.xw;
    u_xlat8.z = u_xlat32.x;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat8.xz);
    u_xlat10.y = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat8.yw);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.z;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat32.x = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat8.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat8.y = (-u_xlat32.x);
    u_xlat8.xw = u_xlat8.xw;
    u_xlat8.z = u_xlat32.x;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat33.xy, u_xlat8.xz);
    u_xlat10.y = dot(u_xlat33.xy, u_xlat8.yw);
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat10.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerR.xy;
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat33.xy * u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat10.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerR.zw;
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.y;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat38 * _Time.x;
    u_xlat9.y = float(0);
    u_xlat33.xy = vec2(ivec2(0, 0));
    u_xlat16_11 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.z + _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat11.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat10.xy = (-u_xlat33.xy);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat35.x = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat35.y = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat35.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.z;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat33.x = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat33.y = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.zw;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.zw = u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat7.zw = u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_18.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_18.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.yzw = u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.y = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.z = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.w = float(0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    vs_TEXCOORD9 = u_xlat8;
    vs_TEXCOORD11 = u_xlat16_4;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD9.xy;
    u_xlat48.xy = vs_TEXCOORD9.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD11.xyz;
    u_xlat73 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.w;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy / u_xlat1.zz;
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat73) * u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = (-u_xlat1.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_MixAnimationMap, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat48.xy = u_xlat48.xy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD11.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.w;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy / u_xlat1.zz;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = (-u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat48.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_MixAnimationMap, u_xlat0.xy).y;
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat16_50 = float(0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_50) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _MainColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _MixMapColorLayerR.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_26) * _MixMapColorLayerG.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 0, 0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www;
    u_xlat16_76 = float(1);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_77 = u_xlat16_3.y + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_77 = max(u_xlat16_77, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_77 = min(u_xlat16_77, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_77 = max(u_xlat16_77, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_77 = min(u_xlat16_77, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_77) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = (-u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat9.x = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat9.x = max(u_xlat9.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat9.x);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xxx * u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_77 = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_77 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_77);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_77) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * _MainLightPosition.www;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_72 = _MainLightColor.w;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.w = u_xlat16_72;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat35 = 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat35;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_0.w;
    u_xlat16_11.y = u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xy = u_xlat16_11.xy;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat13.x = dot(u_xlat14.xyz, u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat13.x = max(u_xlat13.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat13.x = min(u_xlat13.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat13.x;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13;
    u_xlat1 = vec4(ivec4(0, 1, 0, 0));
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[0].zxy;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat1.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz + u_xlat15.xyz;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = vec4(ivec4(0, 0, 0, 0));
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;
    u_xlat2.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat2.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].z;
    u_xlat1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat2, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].x;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].z;
    u_xlat5.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w;
    u_xlat5.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat5.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w;
    u_xlat5.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat2.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat5, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz;
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat4.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat4.z = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat23 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat23 = max(u_xlat23, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat23 = inversesqrt(u_xlat23);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat23) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat18.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.xy;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat18.xy * u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat18.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat18.xy = u_xlat18.xy + u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat5.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat19.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat19.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat4.zw = u_xlat18.xy;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_13.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_13.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.yzw = u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat4;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_5;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = float(0);
    u_xlat16_51 = float(0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat16_102.x = float(0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_102.xxx * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _MainColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _MixMapColorLayerR.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xzw + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_51) * _MixMapColorLayerG.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xzw + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat16_153 = 0.5;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 0, 0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.www;
    u_xlat16_4 = float(1);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_55 = u_xlat16_2.y + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_55 = max(u_xlat16_55, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_55 = min(u_xlat16_55, 1.0);

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS

#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD9;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD11;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec4 u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
vec4 u_xlat7;
vec4 u_xlat8;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
vec4 u_xlat10;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
vec4 u_xlat11;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
vec2 u_xlat30;

float u_xlat34;
vec2 u_xlat35;
float u_xlat38;
float u_xlat39;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = vec4(ivec4(0, 0, 0, 0));
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;
    u_xlat2.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat2.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].z;
    u_xlat1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat2, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].x;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].z;
    u_xlat5.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w;
    u_xlat5.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat5.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w;
    u_xlat5.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat2.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat5, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat4 = in_TANGENT0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat4.www * u_xlat6.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat6.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat6.z = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = max(u_xlat38, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].x;
    u_xlat6.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;
    u_xlat6.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat7.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat7.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat8.xw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].yz;
    u_xlat8.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat8.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat6.x = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat7.z = u_xlat8.x;
    u_xlat6.y = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat6.z = dot(u_xlat8.yzw, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = max(u_xlat38, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yzx;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat3.yzx * u_xlat6.yzx;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat3.zxy * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = float(0.5);
    u_xlat6.y = float(0.5);
    u_xlat30.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat31.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat31.xy = u_xlat31.xy + u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.y;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat38 * _Time.x;
    u_xlat9.y = float(0);
    u_xlat33.xy = vec2(ivec2(0, 0));
    u_xlat16_10 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.z + _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.x;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat10.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat10.xy = (-u_xlat33.xy);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat32.x = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat8.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat8.y = (-u_xlat32.x);
    u_xlat8.xw = u_xlat8.xw;
    u_xlat8.z = u_xlat32.x;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat8.xz);
    u_xlat10.y = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat8.yw);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.z;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat32.x = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat8.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat8.y = (-u_xlat32.x);
    u_xlat8.xw = u_xlat8.xw;
    u_xlat8.z = u_xlat32.x;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat8 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat33.xy, u_xlat8.xz);
    u_xlat10.y = dot(u_xlat33.xy, u_xlat8.yw);
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat10.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerR.xy;
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat33.xy * u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat10.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerR.zw;
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.y;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat38 * _Time.x;
    u_xlat9.y = float(0);
    u_xlat33.xy = vec2(ivec2(0, 0));
    u_xlat16_11 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.z + _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat11.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat10.xy = (-u_xlat33.xy);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat35.x = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat35.y = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat35.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.z;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat33.x = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat33.y = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.zw;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.zw = u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat7.zw = u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat9.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.yzw = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.y = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.z = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.w = float(0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_9;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    vs_TEXCOORD9 = u_xlat8;
    vs_TEXCOORD11 = u_xlat16_4;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 300 es
#ifdef GL_EXT_shader_texture_lod
#extension GL_EXT_shader_texture_lod : enable
#endif

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _AdditionalLightsCount;
uniform 	vec4 _AdditionalLightsPosition[32];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _AdditionalLightsColor[32];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[32];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _AdditionalLightsSpotDir[32];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[4];
uniform 	float _DstBlendFactor;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerDraw {

    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * u_xlat16_15.xyz;

    u_xlat16_66 = max(u_xlat16_66, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_66 = min(u_xlat16_66, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz;

    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat12.x = float(2.50999999);
    u_xlat12.y = float(2.50999999);
    u_xlat12.z = float(2.50999999);
    u_xlat13.x = float(0.0299999993);
    u_xlat13.y = float(0.0299999993);
    u_xlat13.z = float(0.0299999993);

    u_xlat2.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat2.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].y;

    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat35.x = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat35.y = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat35.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.z;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat33.x = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat33.y = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.zw;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.zw = u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat7.zw = u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat9.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.yzw = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.y = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.z = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.w = float(0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_9;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    vs_TEXCOORD9 = u_xlat8;
    vs_TEXCOORD11 = u_xlat16_4;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

    u_xlat38.z = float(0.0799999982);
    u_xlat16_3.x = float(0.449999988);
    u_xlat16_3.y = float(0.449999988);
    u_xlat16_3.z = float(0.449999988);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_27.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat34.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat34.xyz;
    u_xlat34.xyz = u_xlat35.xyz + u_xlat34.xyz;
    u_xlat34.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat34.xyz;
    u_xlat35.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat36.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat36.xyz;
    u_xlat36.xyz = u_xlat37.xyz + u_xlat36.xyz;
    u_xlat35.xyz = u_xlat35.xyz * u_xlat36.xyz;
    u_xlat35.xyz = u_xlat38.xyz + u_xlat35.xyz;
    u_xlat34.xyz = u_xlat34.xyz / u_xlat35.xyz;
    u_xlat35.xyz = vec3(ivec3(100, 100, 100));
    u_xlat34.xyz = min(u_xlat34.xyz, u_xlat35.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34.xyz = u_xlat34.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34.xyz = u_xlat16_34.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34.xyz = u_xlat16_34.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34.xyz = u_xlat16_34.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34.xyz = u_xlat16_34.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16_34.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_33;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = vec4(ivec4(0, 0, 0, 0));
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;
    u_xlat2.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat2.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].z;
    u_xlat1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat2, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].x;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].z;
    u_xlat5.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w;
    u_xlat5.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat5.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w;
    u_xlat5.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat2.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat5, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz;
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat4.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat4.z = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat29 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat29 = max(u_xlat29, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat29 = inversesqrt(u_xlat29);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat29) * u_xlat4.xyz;

    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat22.xy * u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat22.xy + u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat5.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat23.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat23.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat4.zw = u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;

    u_xlat16_15.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_15.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz;

    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.w = float(1);

    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;

    u_xlat8 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat7 + u_xlat8;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2.zzzz * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2];
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2 + u_xlat7;
    u_xlat7 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3] * vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2 + u_xlat7;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat4;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;

    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;

    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));

    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;

    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat35.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;

    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat33.xy;

    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));

    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;

    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));

    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;

    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;

    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_9;

    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    vs_TEXCOORD9 = u_xlat8;
    vs_TEXCOORD11 = u_xlat16_4;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emiss;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _EmissColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _MatTexColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _SHTopColor;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainAnimationMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixAnimationMap_ST;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseMainMapWithStraightAlpha;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MainMapAlphaMaskOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MixMapDistortionScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixMapUVDataLayerR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixMapUVDataLayerG;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixMapColorLayerG;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AlphaOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD9;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD11;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec4 u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
vec4 u_xlat5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
vec4 u_xlat7;
vec4 u_xlat8;
vec4 u_xlat9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
vec4 u_xlat10;
vec4 u_xlat11;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
vec2 u_xlat30;
vec2 u_xlat31;
vec2 u_xlat32;
vec2 u_xlat33;
float u_xlat34;
vec2 u_xlat35;
float u_xlat38;
float u_xlat39;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = vec4(ivec4(0, 0, 0, 0));
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;
    u_xlat2.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat2.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].z;
    u_xlat1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat2, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].x;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].z;
    u_xlat5.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w;
    u_xlat5.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat5.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w;
    u_xlat5.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat2.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat5, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat4 = in_TANGENT0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat4.www * u_xlat6.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat6.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat6.z = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = max(u_xlat38, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].x;
    u_xlat6.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;
    u_xlat6.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat7.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat7.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat8.xw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].yz;
    u_xlat8.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat8.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat6.x = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat7.z = u_xlat8.x;
    u_xlat6.y = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat6.z = dot(u_xlat8.yzw, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = max(u_xlat38, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yzx;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat3.yzx * u_xlat6.yzx;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat3.zxy * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = float(0.5);
    u_xlat6.y = float(0.5);
    u_xlat30.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat31.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat31.xy = u_xlat31.xy + u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.y;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat38 * _Time.x;
    u_xlat8.y = float(0);
    u_xlat32.xy = vec2(ivec2(0, 0));
    u_xlat16_9.x = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.z + _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.x;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat9.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat9.xy = (-u_xlat32.xy);
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat33.x = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat9.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat9.y = (-u_xlat33.x);
    u_xlat9.xw = u_xlat9.xw;
    u_xlat9.z = u_xlat33.x;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat8.xy, u_xlat9.xz);
    u_xlat10.y = dot(u_xlat8.xy, u_xlat9.yw);
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat32.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.z;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat32.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat33.x = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat9.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat9.y = (-u_xlat33.x);
    u_xlat9.xw = u_xlat9.xw;
    u_xlat9.z = u_xlat33.x;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat32.xy, u_xlat9.xz);
    u_xlat10.y = dot(u_xlat32.xy, u_xlat9.yw);
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerR.xy;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat32.xy * u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerR.zw;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat32.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy + u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.y;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat38 * _Time.x;
    u_xlat9.y = float(0);
    u_xlat33.xy = vec2(ivec2(0, 0));
    u_xlat16_11 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.z + _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat11.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat10.xy = (-u_xlat33.xy);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat35.x = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat35.y = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat35.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.z;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat33.x = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat33.y = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.zw;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.zw = u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat7.zw = u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat9.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.yzw = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat2.xxxx * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0];
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2.zzzz * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2];
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3] * vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.y = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.z = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.w = float(0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_9;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    vs_TEXCOORD9 = u_xlat8;
    vs_TEXCOORD11 = u_xlat16_4;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 300 es
#ifdef GL_EXT_shader_texture_lod
#extension GL_EXT_shader_texture_lod : enable
#endif

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowParams;
uniform 	float _DstBlendFactor;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerDraw {

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emiss;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _EmissColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _MatTexColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _RimLightDir;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixAnimationMap_ST;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MixMapDistortionScale;

#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec4 u_xlat4;
vec4 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
vec4 u_xlat7;
vec4 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
vec2 u_xlat22;
vec2 u_xlat23;
float u_xlat29;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = vec4(ivec4(0, 0, 0, 0));
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;
    u_xlat2.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat2.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].z;
    u_xlat1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat2, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].x;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].z;
    u_xlat5.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w;
    u_xlat5.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat5.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w;
    u_xlat5.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat2.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat5, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz;
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat4.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat4.z = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat29 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat29 = max(u_xlat29, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat29 = inversesqrt(u_xlat29);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat29) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.xy;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat22.xy * u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat22.xy + u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat5.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat23.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat23.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat4.zw = u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_15.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_15.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.yzw = u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat2.xxxx * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0];
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat7 + u_xlat8;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2.zzzz * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2];
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2 + u_xlat7;
    u_xlat7 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3] * vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2 + u_xlat7;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat4;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_5;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;

layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;

mediump float u_xlat16_20;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_22;
mediump float u_xlat16_29;
bool u_xlatb30;
float u_xlat32;
mediump float u_xlat16_40;
float u_xlat51;
float u_xlat52;
mediump float u_xlat16_60;
mediump float u_xlat16_61;
mediump float u_xlat16_63;
float u_xlat66;
mediump float u_xlat16_67;
float u_xlat71;
float u_xlat72;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = float(0);
    u_xlat16_20 = float(0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat16_40 = float(0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _MainColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _MixMapColorLayerR.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xzw + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_20) * _MixMapColorLayerG.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xzw + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 0, 0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.www;
    u_xlat16_60 = float(1);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_2.y + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_22.x = max(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_22.x = min(u_xlat16_22.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.x = max(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_22.x = min(u_xlat16_22.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_22.xxx;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = (-u_xlat16_22.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat66 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat66 = max(u_xlat66, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat66 = inversesqrt(u_xlat66);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat66) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_63 = dot(u_xlat16_22.xyz, u_xlat16_22.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_63);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * _MainLightPosition.www;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_61 = _MainLightColor.w;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.w = u_xlat16_61;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_67 = _MainLightShadowParams.x;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat5.xy,u_xlat5.z);
    u_xlat16_8 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_8 = u_xlat16_8;
    u_xlat16_8 = u_xlat16_8;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67;
    u_xlat16_9.x = 1.0;
    u_xlat16_29 = (-u_xlat16_67);
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_29 + u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67 * u_xlat16_8;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67 + u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb10 = !!(0.0>=u_xlat5.z);
#else
    u_xlatb10 = 0.0>=u_xlat5.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb30 = !!(u_xlat5.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb30 = u_xlat5.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb10 = u_xlatb30 || u_xlatb10;
    u_xlat16_9.x = 1.0;
    u_xlat16_29 = (u_xlatb10) ? u_xlat16_9.x : u_xlat16_67;
    u_xlat16_29 = u_xlat16_29;
    u_xlat16_29 = u_xlat16_29;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_1.w;
    u_xlat16_9.y = u_xlat16_29;
