    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat11.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat10.xy = (-u_xlat33.xy);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat35.x = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat35.y = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat35.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.z;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat33.x = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat33.y = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.zw;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.zw = u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat7.zw = u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat9.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.yzw = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat2.xxxx * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0];
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2.zzzz * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2];
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3] * vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.y = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.z = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.w = float(0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_9;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    vs_TEXCOORD9 = u_xlat8;
    vs_TEXCOORD11 = u_xlat16_4;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat33.x = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat33.y = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.zw;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.zw = u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat7.zw = u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat9.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.yzw = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat2.xxxx * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0];
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2.zzzz * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2];
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3] * vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.y = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.z = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.w = float(0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_9;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    vs_TEXCOORD9 = u_xlat8;
    vs_TEXCOORD11 = u_xlat16_4;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD9.xy;
    u_xlat38.xy = vs_TEXCOORD9.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD11.xyz;
    u_xlat58 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.w;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy / u_xlat1.zz;
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat58) * u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = (-u_xlat1.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_MixAnimationMap, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat38.xy = u_xlat38.xy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD11.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.w;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy / u_xlat1.zz;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = (-u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat38.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_MixAnimationMap, u_xlat0.xy).y;
    u_xlat16_21 = u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_21 = u_xlat16_21;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat16_40 = float(0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _MainColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _MixMapColorLayerR.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_21) * _MixMapColorLayerG.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 0, 0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www;
    u_xlat16_59 = float(1);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_3.y + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_22.x = max(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_22.x = min(u_xlat16_22.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.x = max(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_22.x = min(u_xlat16_22.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_22.xxx;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = (-u_xlat16_22.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat62 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat62 = max(u_xlat62, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat62 = inversesqrt(u_xlat62);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat62) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_61 = dot(u_xlat16_22.xyz, u_xlat16_22.xyz);
    u_xlat16_61 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_61);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_61);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * _MainLightPosition.www;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_57 = _MainLightColor.w;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.w = u_xlat16_57;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_61 = _MainLightShadowParams.x;
    u_xlat16_61 = u_xlat16_61;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_61 = u_xlat16_61;
    u_xlat16_61 = u_xlat16_61;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat5.xy,u_xlat5.z);
    u_xlat16_5 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_5;
    u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_5;
    u_xlat16_61 = u_xlat16_61;
    u_xlat16_65 = 1.0;
    u_xlat16_9.x = (-u_xlat16_61);
    u_xlat16_65 = u_xlat16_65 + u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_61 = u_xlat16_61 * u_xlat16_5;
    u_xlat16_61 = u_xlat16_61 + u_xlat16_65;
    u_xlat16_61 = u_xlat16_61;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb7 = !!(0.0>=u_xlat5.z);
#else
    u_xlatb7 = 0.0>=u_xlat5.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb26 = !!(u_xlat5.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb26 = u_xlat5.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb7 = u_xlatb26 || u_xlatb7;
    u_xlat16_65 = 1.0;
    u_xlat16_28 = (u_xlatb7) ? u_xlat16_65 : u_xlat16_61;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_0.w;
    u_xlat16_9.y = u_xlat16_28;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xy = u_xlat16_9.xy;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat7.x = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat7.x = max(u_xlat7.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.x = min(u_xlat7.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat7.x;
    u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat16_7;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat16_7;
    u_xlat5 = vec4(ivec4(0, 1, 0, 0));
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[0].zxy;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat5.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat5.zzz * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[2].zxy;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat5.www * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[3].zxy;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat10.zxy * u_xlat12.zxy;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * u_xlat12.yzx;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat67 = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat67 = inversesqrt(u_xlat67);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat67) * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat10.zxy * u_xlat12.yzx;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat10.yzx * u_xlat12.zxy;
    u_xlat13.xyz = (-u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz + u_xlat13.xyz;
    u_xlat67 = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat67 = inversesqrt(u_xlat67);
    u_xlat11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat67) * u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat10.y = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat10.z = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat48 = inversesqrt(u_xlat48);
    u_xlat10.xy = vec2(u_xlat48) * u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat10.xy = u_xlat10.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10.xy = u_xlat10.xy + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = vec3(ivec3(0, 0, 0));
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = vec3(ivec3(0, 0, 0));
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_9.yyy;
    u_xlat16_9.xzw = u_xlat16_9.xxx * u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_7);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xzw * u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_61 = u_xlat16_9.y + _SHshadow;
    u_xlat16_61 = max(u_xlat16_61, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_61 = min(u_xlat16_61, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_61);

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[20];
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emiss;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _EmissColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _MatTexColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixAnimationMap_ST;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MixMapDistortionScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixMapUVDataLayerR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixMapUVDataLayerG;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixMapColorLayerR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MixMapColorLayerG;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AlphaOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec4 u_xlat4;
vec4 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
vec4 u_xlat7;
vec4 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
vec2 u_xlat22;
vec2 u_xlat23;
float u_xlat29;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = vec4(ivec4(0, 0, 0, 0));
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;
    u_xlat2.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat2.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].z;
    u_xlat1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat2, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].x;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].z;
    u_xlat5.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w;
    u_xlat5.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat5.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w;
    u_xlat5.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat2.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat5, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz;
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat4.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat4.z = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat29 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat29 = max(u_xlat29, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat29 = inversesqrt(u_xlat29);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat29) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.xy;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat22.xy * u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat22.xy + u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat5.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat23.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat23.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat4.zw = u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_15.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_15.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.yzw = u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat2.xxxx * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0];
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat7 + u_xlat8;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat2.zzzz * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2];
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat7 + u_xlat8;
    u_xlat8 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3] * vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat7 + u_xlat8;
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat7;
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat7;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat4;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_5;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

#endif

bool u_xlatb182;
float u_xlat184;
mediump float u_xlat16_184;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = float(0);
    u_xlat16_48 = float(0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat16_96.x = float(0);

    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].x;

    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].z;
    u_xlat5.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w;
    u_xlat5.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat5.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w;
    u_xlat5.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat2.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat5, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat4 = in_TANGENT0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat4.www * u_xlat6.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat6.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat6.z = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = max(u_xlat38, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].x;
    u_xlat6.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;
    u_xlat6.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat7.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat7.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat8.xw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].yz;
    u_xlat8.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat8.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat6.x = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat7.z = u_xlat8.x;
    u_xlat6.y = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat6.z = dot(u_xlat8.yzw, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = max(u_xlat38, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yzx;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat3.yzx * u_xlat6.yzx;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat3.zxy * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = float(0.5);
    u_xlat6.y = float(0.5);
    u_xlat30.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat31.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat31.xy = u_xlat31.xy + u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.y;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat38 * _Time.x;
    u_xlat8.y = float(0);
    u_xlat32.xy = vec2(ivec2(0, 0));
    u_xlat16_9.x = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.z + _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.x;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat9.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat9.xy = (-u_xlat32.xy);
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat33.x = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat9.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat9.y = (-u_xlat33.x);
    u_xlat9.xw = u_xlat9.xw;
    u_xlat9.z = u_xlat33.x;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10);

    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat8.xy, u_xlat9.xz);
    u_xlat10.y = dot(u_xlat8.xy, u_xlat9.yw);
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat32.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy;

    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.z;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;

    u_xlat32.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat32.xy;

    u_xlat9.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat9.y = (-u_xlat33.x);

    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + u_xlat10;

    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat38 * _Time.x;

    u_xlat16_11 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.z + _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.x;

    u_xlat39 = float(2);

    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));

    u_xlat6.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.x = float(0.0);

    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;

    u_xlat10 = u_xlat2.xxxx * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0];
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat2.zzzz * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2];
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3] * vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);

    u_xlat16_4.w = float(0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_9;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat10;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    vs_TEXCOORD9 = u_xlat8;
    vs_TEXCOORD11 = u_xlat16_4;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.z;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat33.x = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat33.y = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.zw;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.zw = u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat7.zw = u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat9.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.yzw = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat2.xxxx * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0];
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat2.zzzz * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2];
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3] * vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.y = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.z = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.w = float(0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_9;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat10;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    vs_TEXCOORD9 = u_xlat8;
    vs_TEXCOORD11 = u_xlat16_4;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD9.xy;
    u_xlat92.xy = vs_TEXCOORD9.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD11.xyz;
    u_xlat139 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.w;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy / u_xlat1.zz;
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat139) * u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = (-u_xlat1.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_MixAnimationMap, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat92.xy = u_xlat92.xy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD11.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.w;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy / u_xlat1.zz;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = (-u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat92.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_MixAnimationMap, u_xlat0.xy).y;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat16_94 = float(0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_94) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _MainColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _MixMapColorLayerR.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_48) * _MixMapColorLayerG.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat16_140 = 0.5;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 0, 0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www;
    u_xlat16_141 = float(1);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_3.y + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_5 = max(u_xlat16_5, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_5 = min(u_xlat16_5, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_140 = u_xlat16_140 + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_51.x = 0.0399999991;
    u_xlat16_97 = float(1);
    u_xlat16_140 = max(u_xlat16_140, u_xlat16_51.x);
    u_xlat16_140 = min(u_xlat16_97, u_xlat16_140);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_51.x = max(u_xlat16_5, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_51.x = min(u_xlat16_51.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_51.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_51.xxx;
    u_xlat16_51.xyz = (-u_xlat16_51.xyz);
    u_xlat16_51.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_51.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat144 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat144 = max(u_xlat144, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat144 = inversesqrt(u_xlat144);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat144) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_145 = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_145 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_145);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_145) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * _MainLightPosition.www;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_138 = _MainLightColor.w;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.w = u_xlat16_138;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12 = _MainLightShadowParams.x;
    u_xlat16_12 = u_xlat16_12;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12 = u_xlat16_12;
    u_xlat16_12 = u_xlat16_12;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat9.xy,u_xlat9.z);
    u_xlat16_144 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_144 = u_xlat16_144;
    u_xlat16_144 = u_xlat16_144;
    u_xlat16_12 = u_xlat16_12;
    u_xlat16_13.x = 1.0;
    u_xlat16_59 = (-u_xlat16_12);
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_59 + u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_59 = u_xlat16_144 * u_xlat16_12;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_59 + u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb10 = !!(0.0>=u_xlat9.z);
#else
    u_xlatb10 = 0.0>=u_xlat9.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb14 = !!(u_xlat9.z>=1.0);
#else

    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].z;
    u_xlat1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat2, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].x;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].z;
    u_xlat5.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w;
    u_xlat5.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat5.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w;
    u_xlat5.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat2.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat5, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz;
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat4.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat4.z = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat29 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat29 = max(u_xlat29, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat29 = inversesqrt(u_xlat29);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat29) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.xy;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat22.xy * u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat22.xy + u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat5.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat23.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat23.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat4.zw = u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_15.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_15.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.yzw = u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat2.xxxx * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0];
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat7 + u_xlat8;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat2.zzzz * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2];
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat7 + u_xlat8;
    u_xlat8 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3] * vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat7 + u_xlat8;
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat7;
    u_xlat7 = u_xlat7;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat4;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_5;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;

vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;

mediump float u_xlat16_67;

float u_xlat72;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = float(0);
    u_xlat16_20 = float(0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat16_40 = float(0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _MainColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _MixMapColorLayerR.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xzw + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_20) * _MixMapColorLayerG.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xzw + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 0, 0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.www;
    u_xlat16_60 = float(1);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_2.y + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_22.x = max(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_22.x = min(u_xlat16_22.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * _EmissColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(vec3(_Emiss, _Emiss, _Emiss));
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.x = max(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_22.x = min(u_xlat16_22.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_22.xxx;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = (-u_xlat16_22.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat66 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat66 = max(u_xlat66, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat66 = inversesqrt(u_xlat66);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat66) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_63 = dot(u_xlat16_22.xyz, u_xlat16_22.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_63);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * _MainLightPosition.www;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_61 = _MainLightColor.w;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.w = u_xlat16_61;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_67 = _MainLightShadowParams.x;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat5.xy,u_xlat5.z);
    u_xlat16_8 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_8 = u_xlat16_8;
    u_xlat16_8 = u_xlat16_8;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67;
    u_xlat16_9.x = 1.0;
    u_xlat16_29 = (-u_xlat16_67);
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_29 + u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67 * u_xlat16_8;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67 + u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_67 = u_xlat16_67;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb10 = !!(0.0>=u_xlat5.z);
#else
    u_xlatb10 = 0.0>=u_xlat5.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb30 = !!(u_xlat5.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb30 = u_xlat5.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb10 = u_xlatb30 || u_xlatb10;
    u_xlat16_9.x = 1.0;
    u_xlat16_29 = (u_xlatb10) ? u_xlat16_9.x : u_xlat16_67;
    u_xlat16_29 = u_xlat16_29;
    u_xlat16_29 = u_xlat16_29;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_1.w;
    u_xlat16_9.y = u_xlat16_29;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xy = u_xlat16_9.xy;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat10.x = max(u_xlat10.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat10.x = min(u_xlat10.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(ivec3(1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat5 = vec4(ivec4(0, 1, 0, 0));
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[0].zxy;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat5.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz + u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat5.zzz * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[2].zxy;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz + u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat5.www * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[3].zxy;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz + u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat11.zxy * u_xlat13.zxy;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * u_xlat13.yzx;
    u_xlat11.xyz = (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz + u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat71 = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat71 = inversesqrt(u_xlat71);
    u_xlat11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat71) * u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat11.zxy * u_xlat13.yzx;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat11.yzx * u_xlat13.zxy;
    u_xlat14.xyz = (-u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz + u_xlat14.xyz;
    u_xlat71 = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat71 = inversesqrt(u_xlat71);
    u_xlat12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat71) * u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat11.x = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat11.y = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat11.z = dot(u_xlat13.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat51 = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat51 = inversesqrt(u_xlat51);
    u_xlat11.xy = vec2(u_xlat51) * u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlat11.xy = u_xlat11.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11.xy = u_xlat11.xy + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = vec3(ivec3(0, 0, 0));
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = vec3(ivec3(0, 0, 0));
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_9.yyy;
    u_xlat16_9.xzw = u_xlat16_9.xxx * u_xlat16_16.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_10);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz + u_xlat16_16.xyz;

#else

#endif
uniform 	vec4 _Time;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD9;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD11;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec4 u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
vec4 u_xlat7;

vec4 u_xlat9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
vec4 u_xlat10;
vec4 u_xlat11;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
vec2 u_xlat30;

vec2 u_xlat32;
vec2 u_xlat33;
float u_xlat34;
vec2 u_xlat35;
float u_xlat38;
float u_xlat39;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = vec4(ivec4(0, 0, 0, 0));
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;
    u_xlat2.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat2.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].z;
    u_xlat1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat2, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].x;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].x;
    u_xlat3.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].y;
    u_xlat3.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].y;
    u_xlat3.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].y;
    u_xlat3.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].y;
    u_xlat4.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].z;
    u_xlat4.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].z;
    u_xlat4.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].z;
    u_xlat4.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].z;
    u_xlat5.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w;
    u_xlat5.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat5.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w;
    u_xlat5.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat2.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat3, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat4, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat5, u_xlat2);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat4 = in_TANGENT0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat4.www * u_xlat6.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat6.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat6.z = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = max(u_xlat38, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].x;
    u_xlat6.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].x;
    u_xlat6.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].x;
    u_xlat7.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].y;
    u_xlat7.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].y;
    u_xlat8.xw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].yz;
    u_xlat8.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].z;
    u_xlat8.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].z;
    u_xlat6.x = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat7.z = u_xlat8.x;
    u_xlat6.y = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat6.z = dot(u_xlat8.yzw, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = max(u_xlat38, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yzx;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat3.yzx * u_xlat6.yzx;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat3.zxy * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = float(0.5);
    u_xlat6.y = float(0.5);
    u_xlat30.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat31.xy = _MainAnimationMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat31.xy = u_xlat31.xy + u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.y;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat38 * _Time.x;
    u_xlat8.y = float(0);
    u_xlat32.xy = vec2(ivec2(0, 0));
    u_xlat16_9.x = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.z + _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.x;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat9.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat9.xy = (-u_xlat32.xy);
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat33.x = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat9.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat9.y = (-u_xlat33.x);
    u_xlat9.xw = u_xlat9.xw;
    u_xlat9.z = u_xlat33.x;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat8.xy, u_xlat9.xz);
    u_xlat10.y = dot(u_xlat8.xy, u_xlat9.yw);
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat32.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerR.z;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat32.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat33.x = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat9.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat9.y = (-u_xlat33.x);
    u_xlat9.xw = u_xlat9.xw;
    u_xlat9.z = u_xlat33.x;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10);
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat32.xy, u_xlat9.xz);
    u_xlat10.y = dot(u_xlat32.xy, u_xlat9.yw);
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerR.xy;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat32.xy * u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerR.zw;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat32.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy + u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.y;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat38 * _Time.x;
    u_xlat9.y = float(0);
    u_xlat33.xy = vec2(ivec2(0, 0));
    u_xlat16_11 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.z + _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat11.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat10.xy = (-u_xlat33.xy);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat35.x = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat35.y = dot(u_xlat9.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat35.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat38 = _MixMapAnimationDataLayerG.z;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat39 = float(2);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat30.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat34 = sin(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat10.xw = cos(vec2(u_xlat38));
    u_xlat10.y = (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.xw = u_xlat10.xw;
    u_xlat10.z = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + vec4(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(2, 2, 2, 2));
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = vec4(ivec4(1, 1, 1, 1));
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat11);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat33.x = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.xz);
    u_xlat33.y = dot(u_xlat30.xy, u_xlat10.yw);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy * u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MixMapUVDataLayerG.zw;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat32.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.zw = u_xlat32.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = _MainTex_ST.xy;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xy * in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat30.xy = _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat30.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat7.xy = u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat7.zw = u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.x = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.y = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.z = float(0.0);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat9.x = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.w = u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.w = float(1);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x;
    u_xlat16_9.yzw = u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat2.xxxx * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0];
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat2.zzzz * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2];
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat11 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3] * vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.y = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.z = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.w = float(0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat7;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat16_3;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat16_6;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = u_xlat16_9;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat10;
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = u_xlat16_0;
    vs_TEXCOORD9 = u_xlat8;
    vs_TEXCOORD11 = u_xlat16_4;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_11;
    return;
}

#endif

  Name "OUTLINE"
  LOD 300

  GpuProgramID 111613
Program "vp" {
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_VCOLOR2N_OFF" "_VTEX_ON" }
"// hash: 2114e9c42af93579
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec4 _ScreenParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump float _Offset;
uniform 	vec4 _ScreenResolution;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
varying mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat10;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_NORMAL0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_NORMAL0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xz = u_xlat0.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat0.xx + u_xlat3.xz;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat0.zz + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat1.y * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat6 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat6 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w * u_xlat1.z + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * vec2(0.00462962966, 0.00462962966);
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat1.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[0].xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[2].xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat1.xyw;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat0.x = sqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 0.00100000005);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat3.x);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / abs(u_xlat3.zzz);
    u_xlat10 = abs(_Offset) * 0.150000006;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 100.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].z;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].z;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].z;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].z;
    u_xlat0.w = 1.0;
    gl_Position.z = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat0);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].x;
    gl_Position.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].y;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].y;
    gl_Position.y = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.yzw);
    u_xlat0.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].w;
    u_xlat0.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].w;
    gl_Position.w = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.zw);
    return;
}

SubProgram "gles3 " {
Keywords { "_VCOLOR2N_OFF" "_VTEX_ON" }
"// hash: 1c60f3f4595ccd71
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 300 es

#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec4 _ScreenParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _OutlineWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Offset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _lightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _FarWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _NearWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _color1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _ScreenResolution;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _OutlineMap;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat9;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = textureLod(_OutlineMap, in_TEXCOORD0.xy, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat1.w * abs(_Offset);
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_NORMAL0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_NORMAL0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat3.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat3.xx + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat3.zz + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat3.xy, u_xlat3.xy);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat9) * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = u_xlat3.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = u_xlat3.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat1.y * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat9 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat9;
    u_xlat9 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w * u_xlat1.z + u_xlat9;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat0.yz = vec2(u_xlat9) * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.150000006, 0.00462962966, 0.00462962966);
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat3.xy = u_xlat0.yz / u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat1.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[0].xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[2].xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat1.xyw;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat3.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat3.xy, u_xlat3.xy);
    u_xlat3.x = sqrt(u_xlat3.x);
    u_xlat3.x = max(u_xlat3.x, 0.00100000005);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 100.0;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat3.x);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / abs(u_xlat3.zzz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].z;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].z;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].z;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].z;
    u_xlat0.w = 1.0;
    gl_Position.z = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat0);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].x;
    gl_Position.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].y;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].y;
    gl_Position.y = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.yzw);
    u_xlat0.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].w;
    u_xlat0.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].w;
    gl_Position.w = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.zw);
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 300 es

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
void main()
{
    SV_Target0.xyz = max(vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
}
Program "fp" {
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_VCOLOR2N_OFF" "_VTEX_ON" }
""
}
SubProgram "gles3 " {
Keywords { "_VCOLOR2N_OFF" "_VTEX_ON" }
""
}
}
}
 Pass {
  Name "ShadowCaster"
  LOD 300
  Tags { "IGNOREPROJECTOR" = "true" "LIGHTMODE" = "SHADOWCASTER" "QUEUE" = "Geometry" "RenderPipeline" = "LightweightPipeline" "RenderType" = "[_RenderType]" }
  GpuProgramID 157361
Program "vp" {
SubProgram "gles " {
"// hash: 3b88408ef73e2427
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 _BaseMap_ST;
uniform 	vec4 _ShadowBias;
uniform 	vec3 _LightDirection;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
float u_xlat6;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _BaseMap_ST.xy + _BaseMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _LightDirection.xyz * _ShadowBias.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat6 = max(u_xlat6, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat6) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat6 = dot(_LightDirection.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat6 = clamp(u_xlat6, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat6 = (-u_xlat6) + 1.0;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 * _ShadowBias.y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat6) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    gl_Position.z = max((-u_xlat0.w), u_xlat0.z);
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw;
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
#define SV_TARGET0 gl_FragData[0]
void main()
{
    SV_TARGET0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
SubProgram "gles3 " {
"// hash: 6c9ce3ebf1fde355
#ifdef VERTEX

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM

};
#endif

in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;

{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _BaseMap_ST.xy + _BaseMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _LightDirection.xyz * _ShadowBias.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat6 = max(u_xlat6, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat6) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat6 = dot(_LightDirection.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat6 = min(max(u_xlat6, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat6 = clamp(u_xlat6, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat6 = (-u_xlat6) + 1.0;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 * _ShadowBias.y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat6) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    gl_Position.z = max((-u_xlat0.w), u_xlat0.z);
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw;
